import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, Divider, Link, Button, List, ListItem, ListItemText } from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const Newsletter: React.FC = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  return (
    <Box sx={{ bgcolor: '#f8f9fa', minHeight: '100vh', py: 4 }}>
      {/* Header with logo and Newsletter button */}
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', sm: 'row' }, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', mb: 2, gap: 2 }}>
          <Link href="/" underline="none">
            <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', fontWeight: 800, color: '#222', letterSpacing: 2, textTransform: 'uppercase' }}>
              RobberBaron Newsletter
            </Typography>
          </Link>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            sx={{ ml: { sm: 4 }, bgcolor: '#111', color: '#fff', fontWeight: 700, borderRadius: 3, px: 4, py: 1.5, fontSize: { xs: 15, md: 18 }, boxShadow: '0 2px 8px #0002', '&:hover': { bgcolor: '#222', color: '#fff' } }}
            onClick={() => navigate('/newsletter')}
          >
            Newsletter
          </Button>
        </Box>
        <Divider />
      </Container>

      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4}>
          {/* Main Content */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
            {/* Featured Newsletter Section */}
            <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 4, mb: 4, bgcolor: '#fff', borderRadius: 3, boxShadow: '0 2px 12px #0001' }}>
              <Typography variant="h3" sx={{ fontWeight: 900, mb: 2, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222', textAlign: 'center' }}>
                Precision Price Alerts, Not Noise
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ color: '#333', mb: 3, textAlign: 'center', fontWeight: 600 }}>
                Institutional-Grade Trading Intelligence
              </Typography>
              <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 800, mb: 2, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222' }}>
                Value Investing Alerts
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#333', mb: 1 }}>
                Based on Benjamin Graham's principles, get alerts for:
              </Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Margin of Safety opportunities" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Net-Net stock candidates" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Intrinsic value calculations" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Quality vs. Price metrics" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 800, mb: 2, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222' }}>
                Options Greeks Alerts
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#333', mb: 1 }}>
                Real-time monitoring of:
              </Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Delta: Price sensitivity" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Gamma: Delta changes" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Theta: Time decay" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Vega: Volatility impact" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 800, mb: 2, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222' }}>
                Advanced Options Trading Strategies
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ color: '#333', mb: 2 }}>
                Access alerts for over 100+ institutional-grade options strategies, including:
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Iron Condor Alerts</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Get notified of optimal setups for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="High-probability ranges" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="IV percentile opportunities" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Risk/reward ratios" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Butterfly Spreads</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Symmetrical setups" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Profit zone calculations" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Break-even points" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Calendar Spreads</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Notifications for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="IV skew opportunities" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Time decay advantages" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Rolling opportunities" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Straddles & Strangles</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Volatility-based alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Earnings plays" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="IV crush opportunities" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Volatility expansion/contraction" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Ratio Spreads</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Directional bias alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Backspreads" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Frontspreads" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Risk-defined setups" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Diagonal Spreads</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Time-based alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="PMCC setups" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Poor man's covered calls" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Rolling opportunities" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444', mt: 2 }}>
                Plus alerts for: Box Spreads, Jelly Rolls, Collars, Protective Puts, Covered Calls, Cash-Secured Puts, Vertical Spreads, Horizontal Spreads, and many more institutional strategies.
              </Typography>
              <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
              <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 800, mb: 2, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222' }}>
                Advanced Technical Analysis
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Bollinger Bands</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Advanced alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Band width expansion/contraction" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="%B indicator crossovers" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Multiple timeframe analysis" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>VWAP Analysis</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Institutional-grade alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Volume profile analysis" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Price action vs VWAP" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Institutional order flow" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Monte Carlo</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Probability-based alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Price distribution forecasts" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Risk assessment scenarios" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Portfolio optimization" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Market Profile</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Advanced volume analysis for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Value area identification" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="POC (Point of Control) shifts" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Volume distribution patterns" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Elliott Wave</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Pattern recognition alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Wave structure completion" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Fibonacci retracement levels" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Wave relationship analysis" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="h5" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, color: '#222', mt: 2 }}>Market Psychology</Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444' }}>Sentiment analysis alerts for:</Typography>
              <List dense>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Fear & Greed indicators" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Put/Call ratio extremes" /></ListItem>
                <ListItem><ListItemText primary="Market breadth divergences" /></ListItem>
              </List>
              <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#444', mt: 2 }}>
                Plus advanced alerts for: Ichimoku Cloud, Keltner Channels, Fibonacci Time Zones, Harmonic Patterns, Wyckoff Method, Volume Delta, Order Flow Analysis, and more.
              </Typography>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>

          {/* Sidebar */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
            <Box sx={{ position: 'sticky', top: 32 }}>
              {/* AdSense Placeholder (Sidebar) */}
              <Box sx={{ mb: 4, display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
                <Box sx={{ width: 300, height: 600, bgcolor: '#eee', borderRadius: 2, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', color: '#888', fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 18 }}>
                  {/* NYT AdSense: Skyscraper */}
                  {/* <ins class="adsbygoogle" style={{display:'inline-block',width:'300px',height:'600px'}} data-ad-client="ca-pub-xxxxxxxx" data-ad-slot="ssssssss"></ins> */}
                  Ad  300x600
                </Box>
              </Box>
              <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, mb: 4, bgcolor: '#fff', borderRadius: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222', mb: 2 }}>
                  Newsletter Topics
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Options Strategies</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Technical Analysis</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Value Investing</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Market Psychology</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Macro News</Link>
                </Box>
              </Paper>
              <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: '#fff', borderRadius: 2 }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ fontWeight: 700, fontFamily: 'Georgia, serif', color: '#222', mb: 2 }}>
                  Trending Topics
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 1 }}>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Greeks Explained</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Bollinger Bands</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Monte Carlo Simulations</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Earnings Alerts</Link>
                  <Link href="#" sx={{ color: '#1976d2', fontWeight: 600 }}>Risk Management</Link>
                </Box>
              </Paper>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Newsletter;
